      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zits attak mirft ar ruhē-\ntu Dwehseli/ un ne irr ne kad\nkahdn Labbumu ehdis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee kohpa apguſlahs\nPihſchlös/ un Tahrti tohs ap-\nkahj.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Raugi/ es finnu juhsfu\nDohmas/ un juhsfu Apnemſcha-\nnu:/ ar ko juhs prett manni\nWarras-Darbu darrat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka juhs fazzifeet: Kur\nirr ta Leel-Kunga Nams? un\nkur irr to Besdeewigu Telts un\nDshwoſchana?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Woj juhs ne effat tohs\nwaizajſchi/ kas pa Zeltu fezzen\neet? Wojjuhs to patchu Sihmes\nne palihſtat?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas Launajs tohp tau-\npihts us to Deenu tahs Samai-\ntaſchanas/ un tee tohp us to\nBahrsibas Deenn pawilzinatt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas stahstihs winnam\npaschas Azzis winna Zeltu? kas\nwinnu foḣdihs/ kad tas ko darra?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet wiꞥſch tohp Kappā\neenests/ un tam buhs tai Kohpā\nweenumebr palikt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tahs Duhnas tahs Uppes\nwinnum labbi patihk/ un wiꞥſch\nwelk wiﬀus Jilwekus ſew pak-\nkat/ un kas preeſsch wiꞥſcha jaw\nbijufchi tohs ne warr iſskaitiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tad juhs manni tik\nwelti eepreezinajat? un eekſch juh-\nfu Atbildeschanahm atrohdahs\nNoseegums.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad atbildeja Ecli-\nStag Teemaniteris/\nfazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Arrig tam STIPRA\nDEEWAM kahds S\nrajs leeti derr? kad tas\npatcham derr/gudri turredam\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Woj tad tam Wiﬀun\nrenam patihk/ ka tu ta tai-\njees/ jeb buhs tas par labbu\ntu tawus Zeltus par nenosee\ngeem turri?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Woj tad wiꞥſch pree\ntewi bihdamees ar tewi K\nturrehs? woj wiꞥſch ar\npreeſsch Teefas nahks?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neggi tawa Blehdiba\nleela/ un taweem Noseegum\nGalla newaid?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu effi tawus Bra-\nbes Wainas kihlojs/ un t\nRaileeni tahs Dreubes iswilz\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "To Peekuſſuchu tu n-\ndſirdinajs ar Ubdeni/ un effi\nIssalkutcham Maist aisleed\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kur kahds Warrens\ntam bij to Setnmi turreht/\nkam leels Gohds bija/ tam\neekſch tahs dshwoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tahs Atraitnes tu effi\nfchas atlaidis/ un to Bah-\nElkoni irr falausiti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht irr Wirweg\nkahrt tewi/ un Bihaſchand\ntero peepeſchi uṣgahjuſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jeb Tumfiba/ ka tu\n"
    }
  ],
